{"tid":2402782,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"24歲Bella Hadid素顏殘樣嚇親網民","createTime":"2021-02-10T15:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T03:23:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8fb1df57e6628ed333e599db8d07889f657bcf","tid":2402782,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n7gnAwCh7SNkcLokh7xvmWB3G6o=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SFQD7WFGNZHG3OBQZAWDSGQU7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn7gnAwCh7SNkcLokh7xvmWB3G6o%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSFQD7WFGNZHG3OBQZAWDSGQU7M.jpg&h=94ccb4a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國名模Bella Hadid一向出名樣靚身材好，年僅24歲的她正值青春年華，又喜歡於IG貼性感相，吸引多達3,800多萬粉絲follow。但昨日Bella貼出素顏相片，卻因為太「真實」而令網民嚇親，千年道行一朝喪。<br />\n<br />\nBella Hadid貼出新自拍照，並表示：「巴勒斯坦人和荷蘭人。」分享自己的血統。相中的她身穿比堅尼騷弗爆身材，但就未有化妝，細睇之下，雀班眼袋通通現形，殘樣嚇親網民。有網民留言表示她樣子很累，Bella就回應道：「我&hellip;剛剛&hellip;起床&hellip;對不起我的眼袋&hellip;得罪了你。」承認殘樣的確嚇人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IqiMGOdNkZU36Vn665EQiEGrTpg=/802x801/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7M22PJ2KBJENDAPJ2DGFCG4BCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIqiMGOdNkZU36Vn665EQiEGrTpg%3D%2F802x801%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7M22PJ2KBJENDAPJ2DGFCG4BCU.jpg&h=ee188a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_qG1L_OVDcp3m6cdOjd3Kp1PtjA=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CNT5EDHMZFEG3FLT5WPIRH6J6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_qG1L_OVDcp3m6cdOjd3Kp1PtjA%3D%